HEADWORD: Ideographical
<hw>I`de*o*graph"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. F. <ets>id⟦eacute⟧ographique</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to an ideogram; representing ideas by symbols, independently
of sounds; <as>as, 9 represents not the word ⟦ldquo⟧nine,⟦rdquo⟧ but the
<ex>idea</ex> of the number itself</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>I`de*o*graph"ic*al*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
